title: I didnt get a mastery 7 token
body:
I played rank with jax and im m6 with jax. I got a s- but no m7 token. Is it because its S-? Kindly confirm.
Thanks

replies.body: Mastery 7 tokens are a bit tougher!  Per the [champion mastery](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204211284-Champion-Mastery-Guide) guide, you actually have to earn an S or S+.  An S- would not grant a token, but you're super close!
